{"tid":1934902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(皇天) 北京昆明湖罕見漲潮   傳上次漲潮後毛澤東去世","createTime":"2020-03-20T08:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T09:59:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"707bba615935af7de08d0dbdd0841d56575bd1b7","tid":1934902,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2020/03/0e9ab5cf6c6b68a665d0f989f8aacc3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F0e9ab5cf6c6b68a665d0f989f8aacc3b.jpg&h=102d55df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020年3月18日，北京西郊頤和園昆明湖波濤洶湧。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n中共病毒（武漢肺炎）肆虐之下，近日大陸多地出現異常現象，包括罕見大火、強風，以及北京昆明湖出現第四次漲潮，據稱毛澤東、袁世凱和慈禧去世前都曾出現過漲潮。<br />\n<br />\n3月18日，京津冀突發狂風天氣，北京西郊頤和園昆明湖掀起巨浪，波濤洶湧，浪花被風打成水霧襲向湖邊遊人和樹木。<br />\n<br />\n頤和園的前身是清漪園，是清王朝修建的著名皇家園林，園內的昆明湖面積約佔頤和園的四分之三。位於昆明湖中南湖島上的廣潤靈雨祠，俗稱龍王廟，常作為園中的祈雨之所。<br />\n<br />\n有北京老人說，頤和園湖水漲潮反常，是中國又要改朝換代了，「從1884年慈禧太后退居頤和園後，至今約140年間共出現過三次漲潮：第一次是1908年11月初，慈禧死前10天左右；第二次1916年6月初，即袁世凱死前3天；第三次是1976年8月初，毛澤東死前半個月左右。現在潮水又起，難道北京真要出大事了？」<br />\n<br />\n在同一天下午至晚間，京津冀地區遭今年以來最強風襲擊，華北北部陣風可達9～10級，局地瞬時最大風速已達11級，並伴有沙塵天氣。<br />\n<br />\n此外，據多個影片顯示，強風的助力下，北京延慶、通州、房山、平谷，河北的保定、廊坊、滄州、邢台、石家莊、衡水、雄安，天津的武清、北辰、津南等地到處著火，火勢強勁。目前傷亡不明。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-03-20/3821722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2020-03-20%2F3821722&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=a0bcb379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2020-03-20/3821722</a>"},{"pid":"f1f711847405097a2cbce88013c2c69717667863","tid":1934902,"uid":99828,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"睇完第一句就知係大紀元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04aea5a9546526203e67d16124ab6c334605a0d","tid":1934902,"uid":31447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"念力反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ac1b008d8ab53da45d217d2046a26b430798fb","tid":1934902,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/5394998314/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F5394998314%2F0&h=fc9bd0cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95bc54197dd65144d1eaafa4579044d126c6b2c8","tid":1934902,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"大紀元可否打少啲飛機✈️"},{"pid":"5f8e9d701334b47ca28ab328fa00d0e010fb1a0e","tid":1934902,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95bc54197dd65144d1eaafa4579044d126c6b2c8","tid":1934902,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"大紀元可否打少啲飛機✈️"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"咁佢哋會無咗生存意義"},{"pid":"efbc23c370605df48b747da123301d30d90892b2","tid":1934902,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://blog.xuite.net/haha.jason/zero/19181939/cover600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.xuite.net%2Fhaha.jason%2Fzero%2F19181939%2Fcover600.jpg&h=da4dbac7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}